    "Hosseini et al. [27] propose a probabilistic generative model called multi-aspect time-related influence (MATI) to consider the fact that time includes numerous granular slots.",
    "Liu et al. [28] proposed a generative template-based event extraction method with a dynamic prefix (GTEE-DYNPREF).",
    "GTEE-DYNPREF learned a context-specific prefix for each context by integrating context information with type-specific prefixes.",
